-- Germany's Sued-Chemie, U.S.-Based Ashland Form Foundry Chemicals Venture
-- Mike Gavin
-- 2010-07-15T13:17:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-15/germany-s-sued-chemie-u-s-based-ashland-form-foundry-chemicals-venture.html

          
          
             Ashland Inc. and Sued-Chemie AG
agreed to form a global joint venture to merge their business
activities in the foundry chemicals sector. Each party will hold
a 50 percent share in the venture, ASK Chemicals GmbH, which
will be based in Hilden, Germany, with Sued-Chemie being
responsible for heading operational management.  
          
          


  


        